import jax
import jax.numpy as jnp

def generated_fn(x0, x1):
    v0 = jnp.add(x0, x0)
    v1 = jnp.maximum(v0, x0)
    v2 = jnp.cos(v1)
    v3 = jnp.multiply(v1, v0)
    v4 = jnp.tanh(x1)
    v5 = jnp.sin(v1)
    v6 = jnp.subtract(v1, v3)
    v7 = jnp.maximum(v5, x0)
    v8 = jnp.subtract(v4, v4)
    v9 = jnp.multiply(v5, v8)
    return v9
